## Dejando el paquete guapo con {pkgdown}

```r
install.packages("pkgdown")`
```

### {pkgdown}: `use_pkgdown()`, `build_site()`, `use_github_pages()` y `use_github_links()`

```r
use_pkgdown()
use_github_pages()
use_github_links()
```

